=head1 NAME

acme-test-localetextdomainifenv - Test Locale::TextDomain::IfEnv

=head1 VERSION

This document describes version 0.001 of acme-test-localetextdomainifenv (from Perl distribution Acme-Test-LocaleTextDomainIfEnv), released on 2019-12-26.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

English:

 % acme-test-localetextdomainifenv
 Hello, world!

Indonesian (not in effect yet without PERL_LOCALE_TEXTDOMAIN_IFENV):

 % LANGUAGE=id acme-test-localetextdomain
 Halo, dunia!

Indonesian:

 % PERL_LOCALE_TEXTDOMAIN_IFENV=1 LANGUAGE=id acme-test-localetextdomain
 Halo, dunia!

(Note: LANGUAGE takes precedence over LANG; if you want to set using LANG, check
whether LANGUAGE is already defined in your environment.)

